name: Dansk 06
description: Part of the Dansk collection, Dansk is a Scandinavian brand of home furnishings popular in the sixties. Typical of the fifties and sixties, the furnishing was clean and smooth. The art of that period was also very colorful. I started drawing with markers when I was twelve. With an artist mother, art is a part of my DNA. I did the Dansk series in 2018 and never posted it or tried to sell it. It sat on my computer until now. With the advent of NFT's, I went through my work and decided to show the series first. I've minted the series on Hicketnunc, and they will be featured in a London virtual gallery in Oct.
